Description: A fast, KDE-native desktop music player
 Ferrous is a fast, KDE-native desktop music player with a Qt6/Kirigami
 frontend and a Rust backend. It features gapless playback, folder-first
 library browsing, real-time spectrogram and waveform visualization,
 and Last.fm scrobbling.
